 id="docs-internal-guid-d8ac59c4-ef58-8817-3f07-04e7d06ad9e7"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">In year 2000, the company joined the cargo forwarding business,&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">John Gold Cargo Forwarder</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">, to provide the fastest, most efficient and cost effective logistics solutions to its clients. Because we are the top agent of &nbsp;major airlines, it has now expanded to various major cities nationwide along with its home base in Davao. With the opportunity seen in magnifying the services, John Gold has opened another business branded as </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Cargo King</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> to serve the door-to-door needs of its clients.</span></span><span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br></span></span></div></div>